  "finalSubmissionGuidelines": "<p>1. Please provide a quick video highlighting your solution in action, If English is not your first language feel free to annotate your video with text.<br />\n2. &nbsp;Provide documentation of how you solution works and example of what needs to be done when a new field is added.<br />\n3. Provide your code in a single zip file and do not do a pull request since others will be able to see (and copy) your solution.<br />\n4. &nbsp;It is not required to deploy your app to heroku but you are welcome to</p>\n",
